FacebookPageProvider - Class in org.apache.streams.facebook.provider.page
Streams Provider which collects Page Profiles in the ID List contained in the FacebookConfiguration object

To use from command line,

Launch using:

mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass=org.apache.streams.facebook.provider.page.FacebookPageProvider -Dexec.args="application.conf pages.json"

Supply (at least) the following required configuration in application.conf:
